title: Eduardo da Silva
summary: Eduardo Alves da Silva (Brazilian Portuguese: [eduˈaɾdu dɐ ˈsiwvɐ], Croatian pronunciation: [eduâːrdo da‿sǐlʋa]; born 25 February 1983), commonly known as Eduardo, sometimes nicknamed Dudu,[3][4] is a Brazilian-born Croatian former professional footballer who played as a forward.
